query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  wl.code AS endereco,
  p.sku AS sku_produto,
  p.description AS descricao,
  i.batch AS lote,
  i.quantity AS quantidade,
  i.status,
  i.expiryDate
FROM inventory i
JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
WHERE i.tenantId = 1149002
LIMIT 20;
